        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 18207e15-3ef6-41a3-a342-3c6e638222b6).Image",
        "Description": "Hello Agent,\rit seems someone missed their alarm for the shift and now it is your turn to take over their delivery route. As a bonus I suggest we add a little bit of metal to the order. For the lazy employee we will make sure he gets an alarm he will hear and that will blow his head off.\r\rSo get going agent, you have customers waiting. the reputation of the company is at stake.\r\rGood luck!",
